flexibleContent.heading: In the world of Managed Security Services, there’s no shortage of competition. Sometimes this environment causes us to lose track of our primary focus: protecting organisations from attack. That’s where the MSF comes in.

usps.content: The MSF runs thought-provoking events and proactive engagement with governments, regulators and more.
usps.heading: Events and engagement

usps.content: The group provides a confidential environment for Managed Security providers to share (and learn from) in-depth knowledge and practical experience.
usps.heading: Workshops

usps.content: The MSF harnesses relationships and experience from governments and the private sector to advocate for the Managed Security industry as a whole.
usps.heading: Advocacy

flexibleContent.content: The MSF and its members work together to produce Managed Security industry-focused research, publications and analysis. Get your copy below.
flexibleContent.heading: Register for the MSF, and download our research.

footerCta.content: Our team of experts thrives when tackling complex cyber challenges. If you have one, we want to hear from you.
footerCta.heading: We seek the toughest cyber problems.

guides.guide: MSF Guide to UK Managed Security
Managed Security and 3rd Party Risk Opportunity

cta.content: Learn how we’re helping global organisations take control of their cyber technology.
cta.heading: What we do

items.summary: A single, unified place for complex, disparate data.
A team of data scientists, engineers and analysts.
Learn more about the team behind Prevalent AI.
Whitepapers, blog articles, podcasts and more.
